      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "txt-title",
        "label": "'181 ALU 16-BIT PAIR - joined by three ribbons (links): H8->H11H cascade, H4<->H4H, H5<->H5H. Shunts pre-set: J1H/J2H at 2-3.",
        "position": {
          "x": -60,
          "y": -46
        },
        "rotation": 0,
        "layer": 0,
        "frequencyHz": null,
        "dutyCycle": null,
        "startHigh": null,
        "designator": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null,
        "filled": null,
        "fillColor": null,
        "borderColor": null,
        "startBit": null,
        "mirrored": null,
        "color": null,
        "fontSize": 6,
        "textColor": "Black",
        "program": null,
        "pinMap": null
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "txt-note",
        "label": "Layers 1-5 = optional population. RN1 = BQ/BKILL pulldowns (SIP9 bussed), R1 = A=B pull-up, RN2 = /FOE //SOE //AUXOE pull-ups (elements 5-9 NC), R2 = SRIN pulldown (LSR-safe idle). BKILL is ACTIVE-HIGH. GND on pin 1 of H4/H5/H7/H10; data headers all-signal. Jumpers (1-2 = solo/Addy; switchClosed true = 2-3): J1 LK_CN, J2 LK_ZC, J3 LK_BORROW. Cascade: straight 6-way ribbon, board N H8 -> board N+1 H11, pin-for-pin (GND, /CN8->CNX, /ZOUT->/ZCASC, AEQB<->AEQB, SRIN<-FB0).",
        "position": {
          "x": -60,
          "y": -38
        },
        "rotation": 0,
        "layer": 0,
        "frequencyHz": null,
        "dutyCycle": null,
        "startHigh": null,
        "designator": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null,
        "filled": null,
        "fillColor": null,
        "borderColor": null,
        "startBit": null,
        "mirrored": null,
        "color": null,
        "fontSize": 3,
        "textColor": "Grey",
        "program": null,
        "pinMap": null
      },
